001package armyc2.c5isr.renderer;

003import java.util.ArrayList;
004import java.util.List;
005import java.util.Locale;
006import java.util.Map;
007
008import android.graphics.Bitmap;
009import android.graphics.Canvas;
010import android.graphics.DashPathEffect;
011import android.graphics.Paint;
012import android.graphics.Path;
013import android.graphics.Point;
014import android.graphics.PointF;
015import android.graphics.Rect;
016import android.graphics.RectF;
017import android.graphics.Bitmap.Config;
018import android.graphics.Paint.Cap;
019import android.graphics.Paint.Join;
020import android.graphics.Paint.Style;
021import android.graphics.Path.Direction;
022import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.Color;
023import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.GENCLookup;
024import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.ImageInfo;
025import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.MSInfo;
026import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.MSLookup;
027import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.MilStdAttributes;
028import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.Modifiers;
029import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.PathUtilities;
030import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.RectUtilities;
031import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.RendererSettings;
032import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.RendererUtilities;
033import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.SVGPath;
034import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.SVGSymbolInfo;
035import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.Shape2SVG;
036import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.SymbolDimensionInfo;
037import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.SymbolID;
038import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.SymbolUtilities;
039import armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.TextInfo;

041/**
042 * This class is used for rendering the labels/amplifiers/modifiers around the single point symbol.
043 */
044public class ModifierRenderer
045{
046
047    private static Paint _modifierFont = null;
048    private static float _modifierFontHeight = 10f;
049    private static float _modifierFontDescent = 2f;
050    private static RendererSettings RS = RendererSettings.getInstance();
051    private static int tgTextModifierKeys[] = {2,3,4,5,6,9,10,11,12,13,14,15};
052
053    private static final Object _ModifierFontMutex = new Object();
054    public static void setModifierFont(Paint font, float height, float descent)
055    {
056        synchronized (_ModifierFontMutex) {
057            _modifierFont = font;
058            _modifierFontHeight = height;
059            _modifierFontDescent = descent;
060        }
061    }
062
063    public static SymbolDimensionInfo processUnitDisplayModifiers(SymbolDimensionInfo sdi, String symbolID, Map<String,String> modifiers, Boolean hasTextModifiers, Map<String,String> attributes)
064    {
065
066        ImageInfo ii = null;
067        ImageInfo newii = null;
068        SVGSymbolInfo ssi = null;
069        SymbolDimensionInfo newsdi = null;
070        Rect symbolBounds = new Rect(sdi.getSymbolBounds());
071        Rect imageBounds = new Rect(sdi.getImageBounds());
072        Point centerPoint = new Point(sdi.getCenterPoint());
073        Point symbolCenter = new Point(symbolBounds.centerX(), symbolBounds.centerY());
074        TextInfo tiEchelon = null;
075        TextInfo tiAM = null;
076        Rect echelonBounds = null;
077        Rect amBounds = null;
078        Color textColor = Color.BLACK;
079        Color textBackgroundColor = null;
080        float strokeWidth = 3.0f;
081        float strokeWidthNL = 3.0f;
082        Color lineColor = SymbolUtilities.getLineColorOfAffiliation(symbolID);
083        Color fillColor = SymbolUtilities.getFillColorOfAffiliation(symbolID);
084        int buffer = 0;
085        int alpha = 255;
086        //ctx = null;
087        int offsetX = 0;
088        int offsetY = 0;
089        int pixelSize = RendererSettings.getInstance().getDefaultPixelSize();
090        SVGPath svgMobilityPath = null;
091        String svgMobilityGroup = null;
092
093        int ss = SymbolID.getSymbolSet(symbolID);
094
095        if (attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.Alpha))
096        {
097            alpha = Integer.parseInt(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.Alpha));
098            textColor.setAlpha(alpha);
099        }
100        if (attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.TextColor))
101        {
102            textColor = RendererUtilities.getColorFromHexString(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.TextColor));
103            if(alpha > -1)
104                textColor.setAlpha(alpha);
105        }
106        if (attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.TextBackgroundColor))
107        {
108            textBackgroundColor = RendererUtilities.getColorFromHexString(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.TextBackgroundColor));
109            if(alpha > -1)
110                textBackgroundColor.setAlpha(alpha);
111        }
112        if (attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.LineColor))
113        {
114            lineColor = RendererUtilities.getColorFromHexString(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.LineColor));
115        }
116        if (attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.FillColor))
117        {
118            fillColor = RendererUtilities.getColorFromHexString(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.FillColor));
119        }
120
121
122        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Build Mobility Modifiers">
123        int strokeWidthBasedOnDPI = Math.round(RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI()/96f*1f);
124        if(strokeWidthBasedOnDPI < 2)
125            strokeWidthBasedOnDPI = 2;
126
127        RectF mobilityBounds = null;
128        int ad = SymbolID.getAmplifierDescriptor(symbolID);//echelon/mobility
129        List<Path> shapes = new ArrayList<Path>();
130        Path mobilityPath = null;
131        Path mobilityPathFill = null;
132        if (ad >= SymbolID.Mobility_WheeledLimitedCrossCountry &&
133                (SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.R_MOBILITY_INDICATOR) ||
134                 SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.AG_AUX_EQUIP_INDICATOR)))
135        {
136
137            //Draw Mobility
138            int fifth = (int) ((symbolBounds.width() * 0.2) + 0.5f);
139            mobilityPath = new Path();
140            svgMobilityPath = null;
141            svgMobilityGroup = null;
142
143            int x = 0;
144            int y = 0;
145            int centerX = 0;
146            int bottomY = 0;
147            int height = 0;
148            int width = 0;
149            int middleY = 0;
150            int wheelOffset = 2;
151            int wheelSize = fifth;//10;
152            int rrHeight = fifth;//10;
153            int rrArcWidth = (int) ((fifth * 1.5) + 0.5f);//16;
154            float rad = wheelSize/2;
155
156
157            x = (int) symbolBounds.left + 1;
158            y = (int) symbolBounds.top;
159            height = Math.round(symbolBounds.height());
160            width = Math.round(symbolBounds.width()) - 3;
161            bottomY = y + height + 2;
162
163
164
165            if (ad >= SymbolID.Mobility_WheeledLimitedCrossCountry && //31, mobility starts above 30
166                    SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.R_MOBILITY_INDICATOR))
167            {
168                bottomY = y + height + 2;
169
170                //wheelSize = width / 7;
171                //rrHeight = width / 7;
172                //rrArcWidth = width / 7;
173                if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_WheeledLimitedCrossCountry)
174                {
175                    //line
176                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x, bottomY, x + width, bottomY);
177
178                    //left circle
179                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
180
181                    //right circle
182                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + width - wheelSize, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
183
184                    //SVG
185                    svgMobilityGroup = "<line x1=\"" + x + "\" y1=\"" + bottomY + "\" x2=\"" + (x + width) + "\" y2=\"" + bottomY + "\" />\n";
186                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\"  ></circle>\n";
187                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + width - (wheelSize/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\"  ></circle>\n";
188                }
189                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_WheeledCrossCountry)
190                {
191                    //line
192                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x, bottomY, x + width, bottomY);
193
194                    //left circle
195                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
196
197                    //right circle
198                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + width - wheelSize, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
199
200                    //center wheel
201                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + (width / 2) - (wheelSize / 2), bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
202
203                    //SVG
204                    svgMobilityGroup = "<line x1=\"" + x + "\" y1=\"" + bottomY + "\" x2=\"" + (x + width) + "\" y2=\"" + bottomY + "\" />\n";
205                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\" stroke=\"black\" ></circle>\n";
206                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + width - (wheelSize/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\" stroke=\"black\" ></circle>\n";
207                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + (width/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\" stroke=\"black\" ></circle>\n";
208                }
209                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Tracked)
210                {
211                    //round rectangle
212                    PathUtilities.addRoundedRect(mobilityPath, x, bottomY, width, rrHeight, rrHeight/2, rrHeight);
213                    svgMobilityGroup = "<rect width=\"" + width + "\" height=\"" + rrHeight + "\" x=\"" + x + "\" y=\"" + bottomY + "\" rx=\"" + rrHeight/2 + "\" ry=\"" + rrHeight + "\" />\n";
214
215                }
216                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Wheeled_Tracked)
217                {
218                    //round rectangle
219                    PathUtilities.addRoundedRect(mobilityPath, x, bottomY, width, rrHeight, wheelSize/2, rrHeight);
220                    svgMobilityGroup = "<rect width=\"" + width + "\" height=\"" + rrHeight + "\" x=\"" + x + "\" y=\"" + bottomY + "\" rx=\"" + rrHeight/2 + "\" ry=\"" + rrHeight + "\" />\n";
221
222                    //left circle
223                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x - wheelSize - wheelSize, bottomY, wheelSize, wheelSize);
224                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x - wheelSize - wheelSize/2) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\"  stroke=\"black\" ></circle>\n";
225                }
226                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Towed)
227                {
228                    //line
229                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x + wheelSize, bottomY + (wheelSize / 2),
230                            x + width - wheelSize, bottomY + (wheelSize / 2));
231
232                    //left circle
233                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x, bottomY, wheelSize, wheelSize);
234
235                    //right circle
236                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + width - wheelSize, bottomY, wheelSize, wheelSize);
237
238                    //SVG
239                    svgMobilityGroup = "<line x1=\"" + (x + wheelSize) + "\" y1=\"" + (bottomY + (wheelSize/2) + "\" x2=\"" + (x + width - wheelSize) + "\" y2=\"" + (bottomY + (wheelSize/2))) + "\" />\n";
240                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" ></circle>\n";
241                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + width - (wheelSize/2)) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + (wheelSize/2)) + "\" r=\"" + (wheelSize/2) + "\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" ></circle>\n";
242                }
243                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Rail)
244                {
245                    //line
246                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x, bottomY, x + width, bottomY);
247
248                    //left circle
249                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + wheelSize, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
250
251                    //left circle2
252                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
253
254                    //right circle
255                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + width - wheelSize, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
256
257                    //right circle2
258                    PathUtilities.addEllipse(mobilityPath, x + width - wheelSize - wheelSize, bottomY + wheelOffset, wheelSize, wheelSize);
259
260                    //SVG
261                    svgMobilityGroup = "<line x1=\"" + x + "\" y1=\"" + bottomY + "\" x2=\"" + (x + width) + "\" y2=\"" + bottomY + "\" />\n";
262
263                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + rad) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + rad) + "\" r=\"" + rad + "\" ></circle>\n";
264                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + rad + wheelSize) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + rad) + "\" r=\"" + rad + "\" ></circle>\n";
265
266                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + width - rad) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + rad) + "\" r=\"" + rad + "\" ></circle>\n";
267                    svgMobilityGroup += "<circle cx=\"" + (x + width - rad - wheelSize) + "\" cy=\"" + (bottomY + wheelOffset + rad) + "\" r=\"" + rad + "\" ></circle>\n";
268
269                }
270                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_OverSnow)
271                {
272                        float halfWidth = (rrArcWidth * 0.5f);
273                    mobilityPath.moveTo(x, bottomY);
274                    mobilityPath.lineTo(x + halfWidth, bottomY + halfWidth);
275                    mobilityPath.lineTo(x + width, bottomY + halfWidth);
276
277                    //SVG
278                    svgMobilityPath = new SVGPath();
279                    svgMobilityPath.moveTo(x,bottomY);
280                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(x + halfWidth, bottomY + halfWidth);
281                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(x + width, bottomY + halfWidth);
282
283                }
284                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Sled)
285                {
286                    mobilityPath.moveTo(x, bottomY);
287
288                    mobilityPath.cubicTo(x, bottomY, x - rrHeight, bottomY + rrHeight/2, x, bottomY + rrHeight);
289                    //mobilityPath.bezierCurveTo(x, bottomY, x-rrArcWidth, bottomY+3, x, bottomY+rrHeight);
290
291                    mobilityPath.lineTo(x + width, bottomY + rrHeight);
292
293                    mobilityPath.cubicTo(x + width, bottomY + rrHeight, x + width + rrHeight, bottomY + rrHeight/2, x + width, bottomY);
294                    //shapeMobility.curveTo(x + width, bottomY + rrHeight, x+ width + rrArcWidth, bottomY+3, x + width, bottomY);
295
296                    //SVG
297                    svgMobilityPath = new SVGPath();
298                    svgMobilityPath.moveTo(x, bottomY);
299                    svgMobilityPath.bezierCurveTo(x, bottomY, x - rrHeight, bottomY + rrHeight/2, x, bottomY + rrHeight);
300                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(x + width, bottomY + rrHeight);
301                    svgMobilityPath.bezierCurveTo(x + width, bottomY + rrHeight, x + width + rrHeight, bottomY + rrHeight/2, x + width, bottomY);
302
303                }
304                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_PackAnimals)
305                {
306                    centerX = Math.round(RectUtilities.getCenterX(symbolBounds));
307                    int angleWidth = rrHeight / 2;
308                    mobilityPath.moveTo(centerX, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
309                    mobilityPath.lineTo(centerX - angleWidth, bottomY);
310                    mobilityPath.lineTo(centerX - angleWidth*2, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
311
312                    mobilityPath.moveTo(centerX, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
313                    mobilityPath.lineTo(centerX + angleWidth, bottomY);
314                    mobilityPath.lineTo(centerX + angleWidth*2, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
315
316                    //SVG
317                    svgMobilityPath = new SVGPath();
318                    svgMobilityPath.moveTo(centerX, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
319                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(centerX - angleWidth, bottomY);
320                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(centerX - angleWidth*2, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
321
322                    svgMobilityPath.moveTo(centerX, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
323                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(centerX + angleWidth, bottomY);
324                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(centerX + angleWidth*2, bottomY + rrHeight + 2);
325                }
326                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Barge)
327                {
328                    centerX = Math.round(RectUtilities.getCenterX(symbolBounds));
329                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x + width, bottomY, x, bottomY);
330                    //var line = new SO.Line(x + width, bottomY,x, bottomY);
331
332                    float quarterX = (centerX - x) / 2;
333                    //var quarterY = (((bottomY + rrHeight) - bottomY)/2);
334
335                    mobilityPath.moveTo(x, bottomY);
336                    mobilityPath.cubicTo(x + quarterX, bottomY + rrHeight, centerX + quarterX, bottomY + rrHeight, x + width, bottomY);
337                    //shapes.push(new SO.BCurve(x, bottomY,x+quarterX, bottomY+rrHeight, centerX + quarterX, bottomY + rrHeight, x + width, bottomY));
338
339                    //SVG
340                    svgMobilityPath = new SVGPath();
341                    svgMobilityPath.moveTo(x + width, bottomY);
342                    svgMobilityPath.lineTo(x, bottomY);
343                    svgMobilityPath.moveTo(x, bottomY);
344                    svgMobilityPath.bezierCurveTo(x + quarterX, bottomY + rrHeight, centerX + quarterX, bottomY + rrHeight, x + width, bottomY);
345                }
346
347                else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_Amphibious)
348                {
349                    float incrementX = width / 7;
350                    middleY = (bottomY + (rrHeight / 2));
351
352                    x = Math.round(x + (incrementX / 2));
353                    float r = Math.round(incrementX / 2);
354
355                    //mobilityPath.arcTo(oval, sAngle, sAngle, moveTo);
356                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x, middleY, r, 180, 180);
357                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x + incrementX, middleY, r, 180, -180, false);
358                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x + incrementX * 2, middleY, r, 180, 180, false);
359                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x + incrementX * 3, middleY, r, 180, -180, false);
360                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x + incrementX * 4, middleY, r, 180, 180, false);
361                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x + incrementX * 5, middleY, r, 180, -180, false);
362                    PathUtilities.arc(mobilityPath, x + incrementX * 6, middleY, r, 180, 180, false);
363
364                    //SVG
365                    x = symbolBounds.left + 1;
366                    svgMobilityGroup = "<path d=\"M" + x + " " + middleY + " ";
367                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + x + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + incrementX) + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + incrementX) + " " + middleY + " ";
368                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + (x + incrementX) + " " + (bottomY + rrHeight) + " " + (x + (incrementX * 2)) + " " + (bottomY + rrHeight) + " " + (x + (incrementX*2)) + " " + middleY + " ";
369                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + (x + (incrementX*2))  + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + (incrementX*3)) + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + incrementX*3) + " " + middleY + " ";
370                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + (x + (incrementX*3)) + " " + (bottomY + rrHeight) + " " + (x + (incrementX * 4)) + " " + (bottomY + rrHeight) + " " + (x + (incrementX*4)) + " " + middleY + " ";
371                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + (x + (incrementX*4))  + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + (incrementX*5)) + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + incrementX*5) + " " + middleY + " ";
372                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + (x + (incrementX*5)) + " " + (bottomY + rrHeight) + " " + (x + (incrementX * 6)) + " " + (bottomY + rrHeight) + " " + (x + (incrementX*6)) + " " + middleY + " ";
373                    svgMobilityGroup += "C " + (x + (incrementX*6))  + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + (incrementX*7)) + " " + bottomY + " " + (x + incrementX*7) + " " + middleY + " ";
374                    svgMobilityGroup += "\"/>";
375
376
377                }
378
379                if(svgMobilityGroup != null)
380                    svgMobilityGroup = "<g stroke-width=\"" + strokeWidthBasedOnDPI + "\" fill=\"none\"" + " stroke=\"" + RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(lineColor,false) + "\"" + ">\n" + svgMobilityGroup + "</g>\n";
381
382            }
383            //Draw Towed Array Sonar
384            if ((ad == SymbolID.Mobility_ShortTowedArray || ad == SymbolID.Mobility_LongTowedArray) &&
385                    SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.AG_AUX_EQUIP_INDICATOR)) {
386                int boxHeight = (int) ((rrHeight * 0.8f) + 0.5f);
387                bottomY = y + height + (boxHeight / 7);
388                mobilityPathFill = new Path();
389                offsetY = boxHeight / 7;//1;
390                centerX = Math.round(symbolBounds.left + (symbolBounds.right - symbolBounds.left) / 2);
391                int squareOffset = Math.round(boxHeight * 0.5f);
392                middleY = ((boxHeight / 2) + bottomY) + offsetY;//+1 for offset from symbol
393                if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_ShortTowedArray) {
394                    //subtract 0.5 because lines 1 pixel thick get aliased into
395                    //a line two pixels wide.
396                    //line
397                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, centerX - 1, bottomY - 1, centerX - 1, bottomY + offsetY + boxHeight + offsetY);
398                    //shapes.push(new SO.Line(centerX-1,bottomY-1,centerX-1, bottomY + rrHeight + 3));
399                    //shapeLines.append(new Line2D.Double(centerX,bottomY - 2,centerX, bottomY + rrHeight + 1), false);
400                    //line
401                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x, middleY, x + width, middleY);
402                    //shapes.push(new SO.Line(x,middleY,x + width, middleY));
403                    //shapeLines.append(new Line2D.Double(x,middleY,x + width, middleY), false);
404                    //square
405                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(x - squareOffset, bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
406                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(x-squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
407                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(x-squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
408                    //square
409                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(Math.round(centerX - squareOffset), bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
410                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(Math.round(centerX-squareOffset), bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
411                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(centerX-squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
412                    //square
413                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(x + width - squareOffset, bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
414                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(x + width - squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
415                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(x + width - squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
416
417                    //SVG
418                    String svgColor = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(lineColor,false);
419                    svgMobilityGroup = "<line x1=\"" + (centerX - 1) + "\" y1=\"" + (bottomY - 1) + "\" x2=\"" + (centerX - 1) + "\" y2=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY + boxHeight + offsetY) + "\" stroke=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"" + strokeWidthBasedOnDPI + "\" />\n";
420                    svgMobilityGroup += "<line x1=\"" + (x) + "\" y1=\"" + (middleY) + "\" x2=\"" + (x + width) + "\" y2=\"" + (middleY) + "\" stroke=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"" + strokeWidthBasedOnDPI + "\" />\n";
421                    svgMobilityGroup += "<rect width=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" height=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" x=\"" + (x - squareOffset) + "\" y=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY) + "\" fill=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"0\"/>\n";
422                    svgMobilityGroup += "<rect width=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" height=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" x=\"" + (centerX - squareOffset) + "\" y=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY) + "\" fill=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"0\"/>\n";
423                    svgMobilityGroup += "<rect width=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" height=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" x=\"" + (x + width - squareOffset) + "\" y=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY) + "\" fill=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"0\"/>\n";

426                } else if (ad == SymbolID.Mobility_LongTowedArray) {
427                    int leftX = x + (centerX - x) / 2,
428                            rightX = centerX + (x + width - centerX) / 2;
429
430                    //line vertical left
431                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, leftX, bottomY - 1, leftX, bottomY + offsetY + boxHeight + offsetY);
432                    //shapes.push(new SO.Line(leftX,bottomY - 1,leftX, bottomY + rrHeight + 3));

436                    //shapes.push(new SO.Line(rightX,bottomY - 1,rightX, bottomY + rrHeight + 3));
437                    //shapeLines.append(new Line2D.Double(rightX,bottomY - 2,rightX, bottomY + rrHeight + 1), false);
438                    //line horizontal
439                    PathUtilities.addLine(mobilityPath, x, middleY, x + width, middleY);
440                    //shapes.push(new SO.Line(x,middleY,x + width, middleY));
441                    //shapeLines.append(new Line2D.Double(x,middleY,x + width, middleY), false);
442                    //square left
443                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(x - squareOffset, bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
444                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(x-squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
445                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(x-squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
446                    //square middle
447                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(centerX - squareOffset, bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
448                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(centerX-squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
449                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(centerX-squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
450                    //square right
451                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(x + width - squareOffset, bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
452                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(x + width - squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
453                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(x + width - squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
454                    //square middle left
455                    mobilityPathFill.addRect(PathUtilities.makeRectF(leftX - squareOffset, bottomY + offsetY, boxHeight, boxHeight), Direction.CW);
456                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(leftX - squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
457                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(leftX - squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
458                    //square middle right

460                    //shapes.push(new SO.Rectangle(rightX - squareOffset, bottomY+offsetY, 5, 5));
461                    //shapeSquares.append(new Rectangle2D.Double(rightX - squareOffset, bottomY, 5, 5), false);
462

465                    svgMobilityGroup = "<line x1=\"" + (leftX) + "\" y1=\"" + (bottomY - 1) + "\" x2=\"" + (leftX) + "\" y2=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY + boxHeight + offsetY) + "\" stroke=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"" + strokeWidthBasedOnDPI + "\" />\n";
466                    svgMobilityGroup += "<line x1=\"" + (rightX) + "\" y1=\"" + (bottomY - 1) + "\" x2=\"" + (rightX) + "\" y2=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY + boxHeight + offsetY) + "\" stroke=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"" + strokeWidthBasedOnDPI + "\" />\n";

469                    svgMobilityGroup += "<rect width=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" height=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" x=\"" + (centerX - squareOffset) + "\" y=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY) + "\" fill=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"0\"/>\n";

471                    svgMobilityGroup += "<rect width=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" height=\"" + (boxHeight) + "\" x=\"" + (leftX - squareOffset) + "\" y=\"" + (bottomY + offsetY) + "\" fill=\"" + svgColor + "\" stroke-width=\"0\"/>\n";

515            int af = SymbolID.getAffiliation(symbolID);

519            double sideOffset = 0;

521            double right = symbolBounds.left + symbolBounds.width();
522

524            {

526                sideOffset = (right - left)*0.3583513488109785;
527                //left = symbolBounds.getCenterX() - ((symbolBounds.getWidth() / 2) * 0.66420458);
528                //right = symbolBounds.getCenterX() + ((symbolBounds.getWidth() / 2) * 0.66420458);
529            }

531            {
532                centerOffset = (symbolBounds.height()*0.25378787878787878);
533                sideOffset = (right - left)*0.2051402812352822;
534            }
535            if(SymbolUtilities.isReality(symbolID) || SymbolUtilities.isSimulation(symbolID))
536            {
537                if(af==SymbolID.StandardIdentity_Affiliation_Friend || af==SymbolID.StandardIdentity_Affiliation_AssumedFriend)
538                {//hexagon friend/assumed friend
539                    centerOffset = (symbolBounds.height()*0.08);
540                    sideOffset = (right - left)*0.282714524168219;//(symbolBounds.getHeight()*0.29);
541                }
542                else if(af==SymbolID.StandardIdentity_Affiliation_Hostile_Faker || af==SymbolID.StandardIdentity_Affiliation_Suspect_Joker)
543                {//diamond hostile/suspect
544
545                    left = symbolBounds.centerX() - ((symbolBounds.width() / 2) * 1.0653694149);//1.07);//1.0653694149);
546                    right = symbolBounds.centerX() + ((symbolBounds.width() / 2) * 1.0653694149);//1.07);//1.0653694149);
547
548                    centerOffset = (symbolBounds.height()*0.08);//0.0751139601139601
549                    sideOffset = (right - left)*0.4923255424955992;
550                }
551            }
552            else//Exercise
553            {
554                //hexagon
555                if(af!=SymbolID.StandardIdentity_Affiliation_Unknown ||
556                        af==SymbolID.StandardIdentity_Affiliation_Neutral)
557                {
558                    centerOffset = (symbolBounds.height()*0.08);
559                    sideOffset = (right - left)*0.282714524168219;
560                }
561            }
562
563            //create leadership indicator /\
564            liTop = new PointF(symbolBounds.centerX(), (float)(symbolBounds.top - centerOffset));
565            liLeft = new PointF((float)left, (float)(liTop.y + sideOffset));
566            liRight = new PointF((float)right, (float)(liTop.y + sideOffset));
567
568
569            liPath.moveTo(liTop.x, liTop.y);
570            liPath.lineTo(liLeft.x, liLeft.y);
571            liPath.moveTo(liTop.x, liTop.y);
572            liPath.lineTo(liRight.x, liRight.y);//*/
573
574
575            liBounds = new RectF(liLeft.x, liTop.y, liRight.x - liLeft.x, liLeft.y - liTop.y);
576
577            RectUtilities.grow(liBounds,2);
578
579            imageBounds.union(RectUtilities.makeRectFromRectF(liBounds));
580        }

920                ebTop = symbolBounds.top - ebHeight - 4;
921            }

933            }

936            ebText.setLocation(symbolCenter.x - (ebTextBounds.width()/2), ebTop + ebHeight - ((ebHeight - ebTextBounds.height()) / 2));

947        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Build HQ Staff">
948        Point pt1HQ = null;
949        Point pt2HQ = null;
950        Rect hqBounds = null;
951        //Draw HQ Staff
952        if (SymbolUtilities.isHQ(symbolID))
953        {
954            int affiliation = SymbolID.getAffiliation(symbolID);
955            int context = SymbolID.getContext(symbolID);
956            //get points for the HQ staff
957            if (SymbolUtilities.hasRectangleFrame(symbolID))
958            {
959                pt1HQ = new Point((int) symbolBounds.left + 1,
960                        (int) (symbolBounds.top + symbolBounds.height() - 1));
961            }
962            else
963            {
964                pt1HQ = new Point((int) symbolBounds.left + 1,
965                        (int) (symbolBounds.top + (symbolBounds.height() / 2)));
966            }
967            pt2HQ = new Point((int) pt1HQ.x, (int) (pt1HQ.y + symbolBounds.height()));
968
969            //create bounding rectangle for HQ staff.
970            hqBounds = new Rect(pt1HQ.x, pt1HQ.y, pt1HQ.x + 2, pt2HQ.y);
971            //adjust the image bounds accordingly.
972            imageBounds.union(hqBounds);
973            //imageBounds.shiftBR(0,pt2HQ.y-imageBounds.bottom);
974            //adjust symbol center
975            centerPoint.set(pt2HQ.x, pt2HQ.y);

980        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Build DOM Arrow">
981        Point[] domPoints = null;
982        Rect domBounds = null;
983        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.Q_DIRECTION_OF_MOVEMENT)
984                && SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.Q_DIRECTION_OF_MOVEMENT))
985        {
986                String strQ = modifiers.get(Modifiers.Q_DIRECTION_OF_MOVEMENT);
987                
988                if(strQ != null && SymbolUtilities.isNumber(strQ))
989                {
990                    float q = Float.valueOf(strQ);
991        
992                    boolean isY = (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.Y_LOCATION));

994                    domPoints = createDOMArrowPoints(symbolID, symbolBounds, symbolCenter, q, isY);
995        
996                    domBounds = new Rect(domPoints[0].x, domPoints[0].y, 1, 1);
997        
998                    Point temp = null;
999                    for (int i = 1; i < 6; i++)
1000                    {
1001                        temp = domPoints[i];
1002                        if (temp != null)
1003                        {
1004                            domBounds.union(temp.x, temp.y);
1005                        }
1006                    }
1007                    imageBounds.union(domBounds);

1013        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Build Operational Condition Indicator">

1020            if (mobilityBounds != null)

1023            }

1038                if (ociSlashShape != null)

1072            }

1074            {

1076                tfBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1077            }
1078            if(ebBounds != null)
1079            {
1080                ebRectangle.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1081                ebBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1082                ebText.shift(shiftX, shiftY);
1083                ebTextBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1084            }
1085            /*if (instBounds != null)//part of symbol bounds now
1086            {
1087                instRectangle.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1088                instBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);

1090            if (fdiBounds != null)
1091            {
1092                fdiBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1093                fdiLeft.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1094                fdiTop.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1095                fdiRight.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1096            }
1097            if (liBounds != null)
1098            {
1099                liBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1100                liLeft.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1101                liTop.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1102                liRight.offset(shiftX, shiftY);

1104                {
1105                    liPath.offset(shiftX,shiftY);
1106                }
1107            }
1108            if (ociBounds != null)
1109            {
1110                ociBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1111                ociShape.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1112            }
1113            if(ociBoundsF != null)
1114            {
1115                ociBoundsF.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1116                ociSlashShape.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1117            }
1118            if (domBounds != null)
1119            {
1120                for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++)
1121                {
1122                    Point temp = domPoints[i];
1123                    if (temp != null)
1124                    {
1125                        temp.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1126                    }
1127                }
1128                domBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1129            }
1130            if (mobilityBounds != null)
1131            {
1132                //shift mobility points
1133                mobilityPath.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1134                if (mobilityPathFill != null)
1135                {
1136                    mobilityPathFill.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1137                }
1138
1139                mobilityBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1140            }
1141
1142            centerPoint.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1143            symbolBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1144            imageBounds.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
1145        }

1536                drawDOMArrow(ctx, domPoints, alpha, lineColor);
1537
1538                domBounds = null;
1539                domPoints = null;
1540            }
1541
1542            if (ociBoundsF != null) {
1543                Paint ociPaint = new Paint();
1544                int size = symbolBounds.width();
1545                float ociStrokeWidth = 3f;
1546
1547                ociStrokeWidth = size / 20f;
1548                if (ociStrokeWidth < 1f)
1549                    ociStrokeWidth = 1f;
1550            /*if(size > 50 && size < 100)
1551                ociStrokeWidth = 5f;
1552            else if(size >= 100 && size < 200)
1553                ociStrokeWidth = 7f;
1554            else if(size >= 200)
1555                ociStrokeWidth = 10f;*/
1556                //ociPaint.setColor(Color.black.toInt());
1557                ociPaint.setColor(lineColor.toInt());
1558                if (alpha > -1)
1559                    ociPaint.setAlpha(alpha);
1560                ociPaint.setStrokeWidth(ociStrokeWidth);
1561                ociPaint.setStrokeCap(Cap.BUTT);
1562                ociPaint.setStyle(Style.STROKE);
1563                ociPaint.setAntiAlias(true);
1564                ctx.drawPath(ociSlashShape, ociPaint);
1565
1566                ociBoundsF = null;
1567                ociSlashShape = null;
1568            }
1569
1570
1571            if (bmp != null)
1572                newsdi = new ImageInfo(bmp, centerPoint, symbolBounds);
1573        }
1574        // </editor-fold>
1575
1576        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Cleanup">
1577        // </editor-fold>
1578        if (newsdi != null)
1579        {
1580            return newsdi;
1581        }
1582        else
1583        {
1584            return null;
1585        }
1586
1587    }

1679    /**
1680     *
1681     * @param {type} symbolID
1682     * @param {type} bounds symbolBounds SO.Rectangle
1683     * @param {type} center SO.Point Location where symbol is centered.
1684     * @param {type} angle in degrees
1685     * @param {Boolean} isY Boolean.
1686     * @returns {Array} of SO.Point. First 3 items are the line. Last three are
1687     * the arrowhead.
1688     */
1689    private static Point[] createDOMArrowPoints(String symbolID, Rect bounds, Point center, float angle, boolean isY)
1690    {
1691        Point[] arrowPoints = new Point[6];
1692        Point pt1 = null;
1693        Point pt2 = null;
1694        Point pt3 = null;
1695
1696        int affiliation = SymbolID.getAffiliation(symbolID);
1697        int context = SymbolID.getContext(symbolID);
1698        int length = 40;
1699        if (SymbolUtilities.isCBRNEvent(symbolID))
1700        {
1701            length = Math.round(bounds.height() / 2);
1702        }
1703        else if((SymbolUtilities.isHQ(symbolID)))
1704        {
1705            if(SymbolUtilities.hasRectangleFrame(symbolID))
1706                length = bounds.height();
1707            else
1708                length = (int)Math.round(bounds.height() * 0.7);
1709        }
1710        else if(bounds.height() >= 100)
1711        {
1712            length = (int)Math.round(bounds.height() * 0.7);
1713        }
1714
1715        //get endpoint
1716        int dx2, dy2,
1717                x1, y1,
1718                x2, y2;
1719
1720        x1 = Math.round(center.x);
1721        y1 = Math.round(center.y);
1722
1723        pt1 = new Point(x1, y1);
1724
1725        if (SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.Q_DIRECTION_OF_MOVEMENT ) &&
1726            SymbolUtilities.isCBRNEvent(symbolID) || SymbolUtilities.isLand(symbolID))
1727        {
1728            //drawStaff = true;
1729            if(SymbolUtilities.isHQ(symbolID)==false)//has HQ staff to start from
1730            {
1731                y1 = bounds.top + bounds.height();
1732                pt1 = new Point(x1, y1);
1733
1734                if (isY == true && SymbolUtilities.isCBRNEvent(symbolID))//make room for y modifier
1735                {
1736                    int yModifierOffset = (int) _modifierFontHeight;
1737
1738                    yModifierOffset += RS.getTextOutlineWidth();
1739
1740                    pt1.offset(0, yModifierOffset);
1741                }
1742
1743                y1 = y1 + length;
1744                pt2 = new Point(x1, y1);
1745            }
1746            else
1747            {
1748                x1 = bounds.left+1;
1749                pt2 = new Point(x1, y1);
1750                if(SymbolUtilities.hasRectangleFrame(symbolID))
1751                {
1752                    /*y1 = bounds.top + bounds.height();
1753                    pt1 = new Point(x1, y1);
1754                    y1 = y1 + length;
1755                    pt2 = new Point(x1, y1);//*/
1756
1757                    pt1.x = x1;
1758                    y1 = bounds.top + (bounds.height());
1759                    pt1.y = y1;
1760                    x2 = x1;
1761                    pt2.x = x2;
1762                    y1 = pt1.y + bounds.height();
1763                    pt2.y = y1;//*/
1764
1765                }
1766                else
1767                {
1768                    pt1.x = x1;
1769                    y1 = bounds.top + (bounds.height() / 2);
1770                    pt1.y = y1;
1771                    x2 = x1;
1772                    pt2.x = x2;
1773                    y1 = pt1.y + bounds.height();
1774                    pt2.y = y1;
1775                }
1776            }
1777        }
1778
1779            //get endpoint given start point and an angle
1780        //x2 = x1 + (length * Math.cos(radians)));
1781        //y2 = y1 + (length * Math.sin(radians)));
1782        angle = angle - 90;//in java, east is zero, we want north to be zero
1783        double radians = 0;
1784        radians = (angle * (Math.PI / 180));//convert degrees to radians
1785
1786        dx2 = x1 + (int) (length * Math.cos(radians));
1787        dy2 = y1 + (int) (length * Math.sin(radians));
1788        x2 = Math.round(dx2);
1789        y2 = Math.round(dy2);
1790
1791        //create arrowhead//////////////////////////////////////////////////////
1792        float arrowWidth = 16.0f,//8.0f,//6.5f;//7.0f;//6.5f;//10.0f//default
1793                theta = 0.423f;//higher value == shorter arrow head//*/
1794
1795        if (length < 50)
1796        {
1797            theta = 0.55f;
1798        }
1799
1800        //Adjust based on DPI, potentially replace code above.  Need to try on different screens.
1801        arrowWidth = RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI()/96f * 5.5f;
1802        theta = RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI()/96f / 10f + 3.4f;
1803        //theta = 3.8f;//arrowWidth / 6;
1804
1805        /*float arrowWidth = length * .09f,// 16.0f,//8.0f,//6.5f;//7.0f;//6.5f;//10.0f//default
1806         theta = length * .0025f;//0.423f;//higher value == shorter arrow head
1807         if(arrowWidth < 8)
1808         arrowWidth = 8f;//*/
1809
1810        int[] xPoints = new int[3];//3
1811        int[] yPoints = new int[3];//3
1812        int[] vecLine = new int[2];//2
1813        int[] vecLeft = new int[2];//2
1814        double fLength;
1815        double th;
1816        double ta;
1817        double baseX, baseY;
1818
1819        xPoints[0] = x2;
1820        yPoints[0] = y2;
1821
1822        //build the line vector
1823        vecLine[0] = (xPoints[0] - x1);
1824        vecLine[1] = (yPoints[0] - y1);
1825
1826        //build the arrow base vector - normal to the line
1827        vecLeft[0] = -vecLine[1];
1828        vecLeft[1] = vecLine[0];
1829
1830        //setup length parameters
1831        fLength = Math.sqrt(vecLine[0] * vecLine[0] + vecLine[1] * vecLine[1]);
1832        th = arrowWidth / (2.0 * fLength);
1833        ta = arrowWidth / (2.0 * (Math.tan(theta) / 2.0) * fLength);
1834
1835        //find base of the arrow
1836        baseX = (xPoints[0] - ta * vecLine[0]);
1837        baseY = (yPoints[0] - ta * vecLine[1]);
1838
1839        //build the points on the sides of the arrow
1840        xPoints[1] = (int) Math.round(baseX + th * vecLeft[0]);
1841        yPoints[1] = (int) Math.round(baseY + th * vecLeft[1]);
1842        xPoints[2] = (int) Math.round(baseX - th * vecLeft[0]);
1843        yPoints[2] = (int) Math.round(baseY - th * vecLeft[1]);
1844
1845        //line.lineTo((int)baseX, (int)baseY);
1846        pt3 = new Point((int) Math.round(baseX), (int) Math.round(baseY));
1847
1848        //arrowHead = new Polygon(xPoints, yPoints, 3);
1849        arrowPoints[0] = pt1;
1850        arrowPoints[1] = pt2;
1851        arrowPoints[2] = pt3;
1852        arrowPoints[3] = new Point(xPoints[0], yPoints[0]);
1853        arrowPoints[4] = new Point(xPoints[1], yPoints[1]);
1854        arrowPoints[5] = new Point(xPoints[2], yPoints[2]);
1855
1856        return arrowPoints;
1857
1858    }
1859
1860    private static void drawDOMArrow(Canvas ctx, Point[] domPoints, int alpha, Color lineColor)
1861    {
1862        float domStrokeWidth = Math.round(RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI() / 96f);
1863        if(domStrokeWidth < 1)
1864            domStrokeWidth=1;
1865
1866
1867        Paint domPaint = new Paint();
1868        domPaint.setStrokeCap(Cap.BUTT);
1869        domPaint.setStrokeJoin(Join.MITER);
1870        domPaint.setStrokeWidth(domStrokeWidth);//3
1871        domPaint.setColor(lineColor.toInt());
1872        domPaint.setStyle(Style.STROKE);
1873        if(alpha > -1)
1874            domPaint.setAlpha(alpha);
1875
1876        Path domPath = new Path();
1877        domPath.moveTo(domPoints[0].x, domPoints[0].y);
1878        if (domPoints[1] != null)
1879        {
1880            domPath.lineTo(domPoints[1].x, domPoints[1].y);
1881        }
1882        if (domPoints[2] != null)
1883        {
1884            domPath.lineTo(domPoints[2].x, domPoints[2].y);
1885        }
1886        ctx.drawPath(domPath, domPaint);
1887
1888        domPath.reset();
1889        domPaint.setStyle(Style.FILL);
1890        domPath.moveTo(domPoints[3].x, domPoints[3].y);
1891        domPath.lineTo(domPoints[4].x, domPoints[4].y);
1892        domPath.lineTo(domPoints[5].x, domPoints[5].y);
1893        ctx.drawPath(domPath, domPaint);
1894    }

1896    private static Rect processOperationalConditionIndicator(String symbolID, Rect symbolBounds, int offsetY)
1897    {
1898        //create Operational Condition Indicator
1899        //set color
1900        Rect bar = null;
1901        int status;
1902        Color statusColor;
1903        int barSize = 0;
1904        int pixelSize = symbolBounds.height();
1905
1906        status = SymbolID.getStatus(symbolID);
1907        if (status == SymbolID.Status_Present_FullyCapable ||
1908                status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Damaged ||
1909                status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Destroyed ||
1910                status == SymbolID.Status_Present_FullToCapacity)
1911        {
1912            if (pixelSize > 0)
1913            {
1914                barSize = Math.round(pixelSize / 5);
1915            }
1916
1917            if (barSize < 2)
1918            {
1919                barSize = 2;
1920            }
1921
1922            offsetY += Math.round(symbolBounds.top + symbolBounds.height());
1923
1924            bar = RectUtilities.makeRect(symbolBounds.left + 2, offsetY, Math.round(symbolBounds.width()) - 4, barSize);
1925        }
1926
1927        return bar;
1928    }
1929
1930    private static Path processOperationalConditionIndicatorSlash(String symbolID, Rect symbolBounds)
1931    {
1932        //create Operational Condition Indicator
1933        Path path = null;
1934        int status;
1935        status = SymbolID.getStatus(symbolID);
1936
1937        if (status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Damaged  || status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Destroyed)
1938        {
1939            float widthRatio = SymbolUtilities.getUnitRatioWidth(symbolID);
1940            float heightRatio = SymbolUtilities.getUnitRatioHeight(symbolID);
1941
1942            float slashHeight = (symbolBounds.height() / heightRatio * 1.47f);
1943            float slashWidth = (symbolBounds.width() / widthRatio * 0.85f);
1944            float centerX = symbolBounds.exactCenterX();
1945            float centerY = symbolBounds.exactCenterY();
1946            path = new Path();
1947            if(status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Damaged)//Damaged /
1948            {
1949                path.moveTo(centerX - (slashWidth/2),centerY+(slashHeight/2));
1950                path.lineTo(centerX + (slashWidth/2),centerY-(slashHeight/2));
1951            }
1952            else if(status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Destroyed)//Destroyed X
1953            {
1954                path.moveTo(centerX - (slashWidth/2),centerY+(slashHeight/2));
1955                path.lineTo(centerX + (slashWidth/2),centerY-(slashHeight/2));
1956                path.moveTo(centerX - (slashWidth/2),centerY-(slashHeight/2));
1957                path.lineTo(centerX + (slashWidth/2),centerY+(slashHeight/2));
1958            }
1959            return path;
1960
1961        }
1962
1963        return path;
1964    }
1965
1966    private static SVGPath processOperationalConditionIndicatorSlashSVG(String symbolID, Rect symbolBounds)
1967    {
1968        //create Operational Condition Indicator
1969        SVGPath path = null;
1970        int status;
1971        status = SymbolID.getStatus(symbolID);
1972
1973        if (status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Damaged  || status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Destroyed)
1974        {
1975            float widthRatio = SymbolUtilities.getUnitRatioWidth(symbolID);
1976            float heightRatio = SymbolUtilities.getUnitRatioHeight(symbolID);
1977
1978            float slashHeight = (symbolBounds.height() / heightRatio * 1.47f);
1979            float slashWidth = (symbolBounds.width() / widthRatio * 0.85f);
1980            float centerX = symbolBounds.exactCenterX();
1981            float centerY = symbolBounds.exactCenterY();
1982            path = new SVGPath();
1983            if(status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Damaged)//Damaged /
1984            {
1985                path.moveTo(centerX - (slashWidth/2),centerY+(slashHeight/2));
1986                path.lineTo(centerX + (slashWidth/2),centerY-(slashHeight/2));
1987            }
1988            else if(status == SymbolID.Status_Present_Destroyed)//Destroyed X
1989            {
1990                path.moveTo(centerX - (slashWidth/2),centerY+(slashHeight/2));
1991                path.lineTo(centerX + (slashWidth/2),centerY-(slashHeight/2));
1992                path.moveTo(centerX - (slashWidth/2),centerY-(slashHeight/2));
1993                path.lineTo(centerX + (slashWidth/2),centerY+(slashHeight/2));
1994            }
1995            return path;
1996
1997        }
1998
1999        return path;
2000    }

2002    /**
2003     * uses 2525C layout which shows most modifiers
2004     * @param sdi
2005     * @param symbolID
2006     * @param modifiers
2007     * @param attributes
2008     * @return
2009     */
2010    public static SymbolDimensionInfo processUnknownTextModifiers(SymbolDimensionInfo sdi, String symbolID, Map<String,String> modifiers, Map<String,String> attributes)
2011    {
2012        int bufferXL = 5;
2013        int bufferXR = 5;
2014        int bufferY = 2;
2015        int bufferText = 2;
2016        int x = 0;
2017        int y = 0;//best y
2018
2019        SymbolDimensionInfo  newsdi = null;
2020
2021        ArrayList<TextInfo> tiArray = new ArrayList<TextInfo>(modifiers.size());
2022
2023        int descent = (int) (_modifierFontDescent + 0.5);
2024
2025        Rect labelBounds = null;
2026        int labelWidth, labelHeight;
2027
2028        Rect bounds = new Rect(sdi.getSymbolBounds());
2029        Rect symbolBounds = new Rect(sdi.getSymbolBounds());
2030        Point centerPoint = new Point(sdi.getCenterPoint());
2031        Rect imageBounds = new Rect(sdi.getImageBounds());
2032
2033        int echelon = SymbolID.getAmplifierDescriptor(symbolID);
2034        String echelonText = SymbolUtilities.getEchelonText(echelon);
2035        String amText = SymbolUtilities.getStandardIdentityModifier(symbolID);
2036        int mobility = SymbolID.getAmplifierDescriptor(symbolID);
2037
2038        //adjust width of bounds for mobility/echelon/engagement bar which could be wider than the symbol
2039        bounds = RectUtilities.makeRect(imageBounds.left, bounds.top, imageBounds.width(), bounds.height());
2040
2041
2042        //check if text is too tall:
2043        boolean byLabelHeight = false;
2044        labelHeight = (int) (_modifierFontHeight + 0.5);/* RendererUtilities.measureTextHeight(RendererSettings.getModifierFontName(),
2045         RendererSettings.getModifierFontSize(),
2046         RendererSettings.getModifierFontStyle()).fullHeight;*/
2047
2048        int maxHeight = (bounds.height());
2049        if ((labelHeight * 3) > maxHeight)
2050        {
2051            byLabelHeight = true;
2052        }
2053
2054        //Affiliation Modifier being drawn as a display modifier
2055        String affiliationModifier = null;
2056        if (RS.getDrawAffiliationModifierAsLabel() == true)
2057        {
2058            affiliationModifier = SymbolUtilities.getStandardIdentityModifier(symbolID);
2059        }
2060        if (affiliationModifier != null)
2061        {   //Set affiliation modifier
2062            modifiers.put(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER, affiliationModifier);
2063            //modifiers[Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER] = affiliationModifier;
2064        }//*/
2065
2066
2067        //            int y0 = 0;//W            E/F
2068        //            int y1 = 0;//X/Y          G
2069        //            int y2 = 0;//V/AD/AE      H/AF
2070        //            int y3 = 0;//T            M CC
2071        //            int y4 = 0;//Z            J/K/L/N/P
2072        //
2073
2074        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Build Modifiers">
2075        String modifierValue = null;
2076        TextInfo tiTemp = null;
2077        //if(Modifiers.C_QUANTITY in modifiers
2078        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.C_QUANTITY)
2079                && SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.C_QUANTITY))
2080        {
2081            String text = modifiers.get(Modifiers.C_QUANTITY);
2082            if(text != null)
2083            {
2084                    //bounds = armyc2.c5isr.renderer.utilities.RendererUtilities.getTextOutlineBounds(_modifierFont, text, new SO.Point(0,0));
2085                    tiTemp = new TextInfo(text, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
2086                    labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
2087                    labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
2088                    x = Math.round((symbolBounds.left + (symbolBounds.width() * 0.5f)) - (labelWidth * 0.5f));
2089                    y = Math.round(symbolBounds.top - bufferY - descent);
2090                    tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
2091                    tiArray.add(tiTemp);
2092            }
2093        }
2094
2095        //if(Modifiers.X_ALTITUDE_DEPTH in modifiers || Modifiers.Y_LOCATION in modifiers)
2096        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.X_ALTITUDE_DEPTH) || modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.Y_LOCATION))
2097        {
2098            modifierValue = null;
2099
2100            String xm = null,
2101                    ym = null;
2102
2103            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.X_ALTITUDE_DEPTH) && SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.X_ALTITUDE_DEPTH))
2104            {
2105                xm = modifiers.get(Modifiers.X_ALTITUDE_DEPTH);// xm = modifiers.X;
2106            }
2107            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.Y_LOCATION))
2108            {
2109                ym = modifiers.get(Modifiers.Y_LOCATION);// ym = modifiers.Y;
2110            }
2111            if (xm == null && ym != null)
2112            {
2113                modifierValue = ym;
2114            }
2115            else if (xm != null && ym == null)
2116            {
2117                modifierValue = xm;
2118            }
2119            else if (xm != null && ym != null)
2120            {
2121                modifierValue = xm + "  " + ym;
2122            }
2123
2124            if(modifierValue != null)
2125            {
2126                    tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
2127                    labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
2128                    labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
2129        
2130                    if (!byLabelHeight)
2131                    {
2132                        x = bounds.left - labelBounds.width() - bufferXL;
2133                        y = bounds.top + labelHeight - descent;
2134                    }
2135                    else
2136                    {
2137                        x = bounds.left - labelBounds.width() - bufferXL;
2138        
2139                        y = (bounds.height());
2140                        y = (int) ((y * 0.5) + (labelHeight * 0.5));
2141        
2142                        y = y - ((labelHeight + bufferText));
2143                        y = bounds.top + y;
2144                    }
2145        
2146                    tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
2147                    tiArray.add(tiTemp);
2148            }

3432                pm = modifiers.get(Modifiers.P_IFF_SIF_AIS);
3433            }
3434
3435            if (jm != null && jm.equals("") == false)
3436            {
3437                modifierValue = modifierValue + jm;
3438            }
3439            if (km != null && km.equals("") == false)
3440            {
3441                modifierValue = modifierValue + " " + km;
3442            }
3443            if (lm != null && lm.equals("") == false)
3444            {
3445                modifierValue = modifierValue + " " + lm;
3446            }
3447            if (pm != null && pm.equals("") == false)
3448            {
3449                modifierValue = modifierValue + " " + pm;
3450            }
3451
3452            if (modifierValue.length() > 2 && modifierValue.charAt(0) == ' ')
3453            {
3454                modifierValue = modifierValue.substring(1);
3455            }
3456
3457            modifierValue = modifierValue.trim();
3458
3459            if(modifierValue.equals("")==false)
3460            {
3461                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
3462                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
3463                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
3464
3465                //right
3466                x = bounds.left + bounds.width() + bufferXR;
3467                //below M
3468                y = (int)(bounds.height());
3469                y = (int) ((y * 0.5) + (labelHeight * 0.5));
3470                y = y + ((labelHeight + bufferText) * 2) - (descent * 2);
3471                y = Math.round((int)bounds.top + y);
3472
3473
3474                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
3475                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
3476
3477            }
3478
3479        }
3480
3481        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.W_DTG_1))
3482        {
3483            modifierValue = modifiers.get(Modifiers.W_DTG_1);
3484
3485            if(modifierValue != null)
3486            {
3487                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
3488                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
3489                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
3490
3491                //above X/Y on left
3492                x = bounds.left - labelWidth - bufferXL;
3493                //above X/Y
3494                y = (int)(bounds.height());
3495                y = (int) ((y * 0.5) + (labelHeight * 0.5));
3496                y = y - ((labelHeight + bufferText) * 2);
3497                y = (int)bounds.top + y;
3498
3499
3500                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
3501                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
3502            }
3503        }
3504
3505        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.F_REINFORCED_REDUCED) ||
3506                modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER) ||
3507                modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.AS_COUNTRY))
3508        {
3509            modifierValue = null;
3510            String E = null,
3511                    F = null,
3512                    AS = null;
3513
3514            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER))
3515            {
3516                E = modifiers.get(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER);
3517                modifiers.remove(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER);
3518            }
3519            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.F_REINFORCED_REDUCED))
3520            {
3521                F = modifiers.get(Modifiers.F_REINFORCED_REDUCED);
3522            }
3523            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.AS_COUNTRY))
3524            {
3525                AS = modifiers.get(Modifiers.AS_COUNTRY);
3526            }
3527
3528            if (E != null && E.equals("") == false)
3529            {
3530                modifierValue = E;
3531            }
3532
3533            if (F != null && F.equals("") == false)
3534            {
3535                if (F.toUpperCase(Locale.US) == ("R"))
3536                {
3537                    F = "(+)";
3538                }
3539                else if (F.toUpperCase(Locale.US) == ("D"))
3540                {
3541                    F = "(-)";
3542                }
3543                else if (F.toUpperCase(Locale.US) == ("RD"))
3544                {
3545                    F = "(" + (char) (177) + ")";
3546                }
3547            }
3548
3549            if (F != null && F.equals("") == false)
3550            {
3551                if (modifierValue != null && modifierValue.equals("") == false)
3552                {
3553                    modifierValue = modifierValue + " " + F;
3554                }
3555                else
3556                {
3557                    modifierValue = F;
3558                }
3559            }
3560
3561            if (AS != null && AS.equals("") == false)
3562            {
3563                if (modifierValue != null && modifierValue.equals("") == false)
3564                {
3565                    modifierValue = modifierValue + " " + AS;
3566                }
3567                else
3568                {
3569                    modifierValue = AS;
3570                }
3571            }
3572
3573            if(modifierValue != null)
3574            {
3575                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
3576                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
3577                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
3578
3579                //right
3580                x = bounds.left + bounds.width() + bufferXR;
3581                //above G
3582                y = (bounds.height());
3583                y = (int) ((y * 0.5) + (labelHeight * 0.5));
3584                y = y - ((labelHeight + bufferText) * 2);
3585                y = bounds.top + y;
3586
3587
3588                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
3589                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
3590
3591            }
3592        }
3593
3594        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.AA_SPECIAL_C2_HQ)  &&
3595                SymbolUtilities.canSymbolHaveModifier(symbolID, Modifiers.AA_SPECIAL_C2_HQ))
3596        {
3597            modifierValue = modifiers.get(Modifiers.AA_SPECIAL_C2_HQ);
3598
3599            if(modifierValue != null)
3600            {
3601                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
3602                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
3603                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
3604
3605                x = (int) ((symbolBounds.left + (symbolBounds.width() * 0.5f)) - (labelWidth * 0.5f));
3606
3607                y = (symbolBounds.height());//checkpoint, get box above the point
3608                y = (int) ((y * 0.5) + ((labelHeight - descent) * 0.5));
3609                y = symbolBounds.top + y;
3610
3611                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
3612                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
3613            }
3614        }
3615
3616
3617
3618        // </editor-fold>
3619
3620        //Shift Points and Draw
3621        newsdi = shiftUnitPointsAndDraw(tiArray,sdi,attributes);
3622
3623        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Cleanup">
3624        tiArray = null;
3625        tiTemp = null;
3626        //tempShape = null;
3627        //ctx = null;
3628        //buffer = null;
3629        // </editor-fold>
3630
3631        return newsdi;
3632    }

4097            modifierValue = modifierValue.trim();
4098

4100                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
4101                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
4102                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
4103
4104                //right
4105                x = bounds.left + bounds.width() + bufferXR;
4106                //above Z
4107                y = bounds.top + bounds.height() - (labelHeight * 4);
4108
4109                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
4110                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
4111
4112            }
4113        }
4114
4115
4116        // </editor-fold>
4117

4119        newsdi = shiftUnitPointsAndDraw(tiArray,sdi,attributes);

7364            if(modifierValue != null)
7365            {
7366                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
7367                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
7368                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
7369
7370                //on left
7371                x = bounds.left - labelWidth - bufferXL;
7372                //oppoiste AS unless that's higher than the top of the symbol
7373                y = (int)(bounds.top + ((bounds.height() / 2) - bufferText - descent - (labelHeight * 2)));
7374                if(y <= bounds.top + labelHeight)
7375                {
7376                    y = (int)bounds.top + labelHeight - descent;
7377                }
7378
7379
7380                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
7381                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
7382            }
7383        }
7384
7385        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER) ||
7386                modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.AS_COUNTRY))
7387        {
7388            modifierValue = null;
7389            String E = null,
7390                    AS = null;
7391
7392            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER))
7393            {
7394                E = modifiers.get(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER);
7395                modifiers.remove(Modifiers.E_FRAME_SHAPE_MODIFIER);
7396            }
7397            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.AS_COUNTRY))
7398            {
7399                AS = modifiers.get(Modifiers.AS_COUNTRY);
7400            }
7401
7402
7403            if (E != null && E.equals("") == false)
7404            {
7405                modifierValue = E;
7406            }
7407
7408            if (AS != null && AS.equals("") == false)
7409            {
7410                if (modifierValue != null && modifierValue.equals("") == false)
7411                {
7412                    modifierValue = modifierValue + " " + AS;
7413                }
7414                else
7415                {
7416                    modifierValue = AS;
7417                }
7418            }
7419
7420            if(modifierValue != null)
7421            {
7422                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
7423                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
7424                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
7425
7426                //right
7427                x = (int)(bounds.left+ bounds.width() + bufferXR);
7428                //above V
7429                //y = (int)(bounds.getY() + ((bounds.getHeight() / 2) - (labelHeight - bufferText) ));//android
7430                y = (int)(bounds.top + ((bounds.height() / 2) - bufferText - descent - (labelHeight * 2)));
7431
7432
7433                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
7434                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
7435
7436            }
7437        }
7438
7439        if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.T_UNIQUE_DESIGNATION_1))
7440        {
7441            modifierValue = null;
7442
7443            if (modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.T_UNIQUE_DESIGNATION_1))
7444            {
7445                modifierValue = modifiers.get(Modifiers.T_UNIQUE_DESIGNATION_1);
7446            }
7447
7448            if(modifierValue != null && modifierValue.equals("") == false)
7449            {
7450                tiTemp = new TextInfo(modifierValue, 0, 0, _modifierFont);
7451                labelBounds = tiTemp.getTextBounds();
7452                labelWidth = labelBounds.width();
7453
7454                //right
7455                x = bounds.left + bounds.width() + bufferXR;
7456                //above V
7457                //y = (int)(bounds.getY() + ((bounds.getHeight() / 2) - (labelHeight - bufferText) ));//android
7458                y = (int)(bounds.top + ((bounds.height() / 2) - bufferText - descent - labelHeight));
7459
7460                tiTemp.setLocation(x, y);
7461                tiArray.add(tiTemp);
7462
7463            }
7464        }
7465
7466
7467        // </editor-fold>
7468
7469        //Shift Points and Draw
7470        newsdi = shiftUnitPointsAndDraw(tiArray,sdi,attributes);
7471
7472        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Cleanup">
7473        tiArray = null;
7474        tiTemp = null;
7475        //tempShape = null;
7476        //ctx = null;
7477        //buffer = null;
7478        // </editor-fold>
7479
7480        return newsdi;
7481    }

9162            fdiTop = new Point(Math.round(RectUtilities.getCenterX(symbolBounds)), Math.round(symbolBounds.top - (symbolBounds.width() * .5f)));
9163
9164

9166            fdiBounds.union(fdiTop.x, fdiTop.y);
9167            fdiBounds.union(fdiRight.x, fdiRight.y);
9168

9170            RectUtilities.grow(fdiBounds,Math.round(fdiStrokeWidth/2));

9178                fdiRight.offset(0, shiftY);
9179                fdiBounds.offset(0, shiftY);
9180            }
9181
9182            imageBounds.union(fdiBounds);
9183
9184        }
9185        // </editor-fold>
9186
9187        // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Shift Points and Draw">
9188        Rect modifierBounds = null;
9189        if (arrMods != null && arrMods.size() > 0)
9190        {
9191
9192            //build modifier bounds/////////////////////////////////////////
9193            modifierBounds = arrMods.get(0).getTextOutlineBounds();
9194            int size = arrMods.size();

9197            {

9200            }
9201
9202        }
9203

9205        {
9206
9207            if (modifierBounds != null)
9208            {
9209                imageBounds.union(modifierBounds);
9210            }
9211            if (domBounds != null)
9212            {
9213                imageBounds.union(domBounds);
9214            }

9224                int shiftY = Math.abs(imageBounds.top);
9225

9230                {

9242                        if (temp != null)
9243                        {
9244                            temp.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
9245                        }

9249

9251                if (fdiBounds != null)
9252                {

9255                    fdiTop.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
9256                    fdiRight.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
9257                }
9258

9260                centerPoint.offset(shiftX, shiftY);

9270                    textColor.setAlpha(alpha);

9273            {

9341            }
9342            else if(sdi instanceof SVGSymbolInfo)
9343            {

9345                if(strokeWidth < 1)

9348                String svgStrokeWidth = String.valueOf(strokeWidth);//"3";

9374                    domPath.lineTo(domPoints[4].x, domPoints[4].y);
9375                    domPath.lineTo(domPoints[5].x, domPoints[5].y);
9376                    sbSVG.append(domPath.toSVGElement(null,0f,svgStroke,1f,1f));

9379                    domPoints = null;

9382
9383                //<editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Draw FDI">
9384                if (fdiBounds != null)
9385                {
9386
9387                    int dpi = RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI();
9388                    int lineLength = dpi / 96 * 6;

9398

9400
9401                    sbSVG.append(fdiPath.toSVGElement(svgStroke,Float.parseFloat(svgStrokeWidth),null,1f,1f));
9402                    //sbSVG.append(Shape2SVG.Convert(fdiPath, svgStroke, null, svgStrokeWidth, svgAlpha, svgAlpha, svgFDIDashArray));

9405
9406                newsdi = new SVGSymbolInfo(sbSVG.toString(),centerPoint,symbolBounds,imageBounds);
9407            }
9408
9409
9410
9411
9412            // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Cleanup">
9413            //ctx = null;
9414            // </editor-fold>
9415
9416            return newsdi;
9417
9418        }
9419        else
9420        {
9421            return null;
9422        }
9423        // </editor-fold>
9424
9425    }
