9775                Bitmap bmp = Bitmap.createBitmap(imageBounds.width(), imageBounds.height(), Config.ARGB_8888);
9776                Canvas ctx = new Canvas(bmp);
9777
9778                //draw original icon with potential modifiers.
9779                ctx.drawBitmap(ii.getImage(), symbolBounds.left, symbolBounds.top, null);
9780                //ctx.drawImage(ii.getImage(),imageBoundsOld.left,imageBoundsOld.top);
9781
9782
9783                renderText(ctx, arrMods, textColor, textBackgroundColor);
9784
9785                //<editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Draw FDI">
9786                if (fdiBounds != null) {
9787
9788                    Paint fdiPaint = new Paint();
9789                    fdiPaint.setAntiAlias(true);
9790                    fdiPaint.setColor(lineColor.toInt());/// setARGB(255, 0, 0, 0);
9791                    if (alpha > -1)
9792                        fdiPaint.setAlpha(alpha);
9793                    fdiPaint.setStyle(Style.STROKE);
9794
9795                    int dpi = RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI();
9796                    int lineLength = dpi / 96 * 6;
9797                    int lineGap = dpi / 96 * 4;
9798
9799                    fdiPaint.setPathEffect(new DashPathEffect(new float[]
9800                            {
9801                                    lineLength, lineGap
9802                            }, 0));
9803
9804                    float fdiStrokeWidth = Math.round(dpi / 96f);
9805                    if (fdiStrokeWidth < 2)
9806                        fdiStrokeWidth = 2;
9807
9808                    fdiPaint.setStrokeCap(Cap.BUTT);
9809                    fdiPaint.setStrokeJoin(Join.MITER);
9810                    fdiPaint.setStrokeWidth(fdiStrokeWidth);
9811
9812                    Path fdiPath = new Path();
9813
9814                    fdiPath.moveTo(fdiTop.x, fdiTop.y);
9815                    fdiPath.lineTo(fdiLeft.x, fdiLeft.y);
9816                    fdiPath.moveTo(fdiTop.x, fdiTop.y);
9817                    fdiPath.lineTo(fdiRight.x, fdiRight.y);
9818                    ctx.drawPath(fdiPath, fdiPaint);
9819
9820                    fdiBounds = null;
9821
9822                }
9823                //</editor-fold>
9824
9825                newsdi = new ImageInfo(bmp, centerPoint, symbolBounds);
9826            }
9827            else if(sdi instanceof SVGSymbolInfo)
9828            {
9829                String svgStroke = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(lineColor,false);
9830                String svgStrokeWidth = "3";
9831                String svgAlpha = null;
9832                if(alpha > -1)
9833                    svgAlpha = String.valueOf(alpha);
9834                ssi = (SVGSymbolInfo)sdi;
9835                StringBuilder sbSVG = new StringBuilder();
9836                sbSVG.append(ssi.getSVG());
9837                sbSVG.append(renderTextElements(arrMods,textColor,textBackgroundColor));
9838
9839                //<editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Draw FDI">
9840                if (fdiBounds != null)
9841                {
9842                    int dpi = RendererSettings.getInstance().getDeviceDPI();
9843                    int lineLength = dpi / 96 * 6;
9844                    int lineGap = dpi / 96 * 4;
9845
9846                    String svgFDIDashArray = "" + lineLength + " " + lineGap;
9847
9848                    SVGPath fdiPath = new SVGPath();
9849                    fdiPath.moveTo(fdiTop.x, fdiTop.y);
9850                    fdiPath.lineTo(fdiLeft.x, fdiLeft.y);
9851                    fdiPath.moveTo(fdiTop.x, fdiTop.y);
9852                    fdiPath.lineTo(fdiRight.x, fdiRight.y);//*/
9853
9854                    fdiPath.setLineDash(svgFDIDashArray);
9855                    sbSVG.append(fdiPath.toSVGElement(svgStroke,Float.parseFloat(svgStrokeWidth),null,1f,1f));
9856                    //sbSVG.append(Shape2SVG.Convert(fdiPath, svgStroke, null, svgStrokeWidth, svgAlpha, svgAlpha, svgFDIDashArray));
9857                }
9858                //</editor-fold>
9859
9860                newsdi = new SVGSymbolInfo(sbSVG.toString(),centerPoint,symbolBounds,imageBounds);
9861            }
9862
9863            // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Cleanup">
9864            //ctx = null;
9865
9866            // </editor-fold>
9867        }
9868        // </editor-fold>
9869        return newsdi;
9870
9871    }

9873    private static SymbolDimensionInfo shiftUnitPointsAndDraw(ArrayList<TextInfo> tiArray, SymbolDimensionInfo sdi, Map<String,String> attributes)
9874    {
9875        ImageInfo ii = null;
9876        SVGSymbolInfo ssi = null;
9877        SymbolDimensionInfo newsdi = null;
9878
9879        int alpha = -1;
9880
9881
9882        if (attributes != null && attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.Alpha))
9883        {
9884            alpha = Integer.parseInt(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.Alpha));
9885        }
9886
9887        Color textColor = Color.BLACK;
9888        Color textBackgroundColor = null;
9889
9890        Rect symbolBounds = new Rect(sdi.getSymbolBounds());
9891        Point centerPoint = new Point(sdi.getCenterPoint());
9892        Rect imageBounds = new Rect(sdi.getImageBounds());
9893        Rect imageBoundsOld = new Rect(sdi.getImageBounds());
9894
9895        Rect modifierBounds = null;
9896        if (tiArray != null && tiArray.size() > 0)
9897        {
9898
9899            //build modifier bounds/////////////////////////////////////////
9900            modifierBounds = tiArray.get(0).getTextOutlineBounds();
9901            int size = tiArray.size();
9902            TextInfo tempShape = null;
9903            for (int i = 1; i < size; i++)
9904            {
9905                tempShape = tiArray.get(i);
9906                modifierBounds.union(tempShape.getTextOutlineBounds());
9907            }
9908
9909        }
9910
9911        if (modifierBounds != null)
9912        {
9913
9914            imageBounds.union(modifierBounds);
9915
9916            //shift points if needed////////////////////////////////////////
9917            if (sdi instanceof ImageInfo && (imageBounds.left < 0 || imageBounds.top < 0))
9918            {
9919                int shiftX = Math.round(Math.abs(imageBounds.left)),
9920                        shiftY = Math.round(Math.abs(imageBounds.top));
9921
9922                //shift mobility points
9923                int size = tiArray.size();
9924                TextInfo tempShape = null;
9925                for (int i = 0; i < size; i++)
9926                {
9927                    tempShape = tiArray.get(i);
9928                    tempShape.shift(shiftX, shiftY);
9929                }
9930                RectUtilities.shift(modifierBounds, shiftX, shiftY);
9931                //modifierBounds.shift(shiftX,shiftY);
9932
9933                //shift image points
9934                centerPoint.offset(shiftX, shiftY);
9935                RectUtilities.shift(symbolBounds, shiftX, shiftY);
9936                RectUtilities.shift(imageBounds, shiftX, shiftY);
9937                RectUtilities.shift(imageBoundsOld, shiftX, shiftY);
9938                /*centerPoint.shift(shiftX, shiftY);
9939                 symbolBounds.shift(shiftX, shiftY);
9940                 imageBounds.shift(shiftX, shiftY);
9941                 imageBoundsOld.shift(shiftX, shiftY);//*/
9942            }
9943
9944            if (attributes != null && attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.TextColor))
9945            {
9946                textColor = RendererUtilities.getColorFromHexString(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.TextColor));
9947                if(alpha > -1)
9948                    textColor.setAlpha(alpha);
9949            }
9950            if (attributes != null && attributes.containsKey(MilStdAttributes.TextBackgroundColor))
9951            {
9952                textBackgroundColor = RendererUtilities.getColorFromHexString(attributes.get(MilStdAttributes.TextBackgroundColor));
9953                if(alpha > -1)
9954                    textBackgroundColor.setAlpha(alpha);
9955            }
9956
9957            if(sdi instanceof ImageInfo)
9958            {
9959                ii = (ImageInfo) sdi;
9960
9961                Bitmap bmp = Bitmap.createBitmap(imageBounds.width(), imageBounds.height(), Config.ARGB_8888);
9962                Canvas ctx = new Canvas(bmp);
9963
9964                //render////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
9965                //draw original icon with potential modifiers.
9966                ctx.drawBitmap(ii.getImage(), imageBoundsOld.left, imageBoundsOld.top, null);
9967                //ctx.drawImage(ii.getImage(),imageBoundsOld.left,imageBoundsOld.top);
9968
9969                renderText(ctx, tiArray, textColor, textBackgroundColor);
9970
9971                newsdi = new ImageInfo(bmp, centerPoint, symbolBounds);
9972            }
9973            else if(sdi instanceof SVGSymbolInfo)
9974            {
9975                ssi = (SVGSymbolInfo)sdi;
9976                StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
9977                sb.append(ssi.getSVG());
9978                sb.append(renderTextElements(tiArray,textColor,textBackgroundColor));
9979                newsdi = new SVGSymbolInfo(sb.toString(),centerPoint,symbolBounds,imageBounds);
9980            }
9981        }
9982
9983        if(newsdi == null)
9984            newsdi = sdi;
9985
9986        return newsdi;
9987    }
9988    private static String renderTextElement(ArrayList<TextInfo> tiArray, Color color, Color backgroundColor)
9989    {
9990        StringBuilder sbSVG = new StringBuilder();
9991
9992        String svgStroke = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(RendererUtilities.getIdealOutlineColor(color),false);
9993        if(backgroundColor != null)
9994            svgStroke = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(backgroundColor,false);
9995
9996        String svgFill = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(color,false);
9997        String svgStrokeWidth = "2";//String.valueOf(RendererSettings.getInstance().getTextOutlineWidth());
9998        for (TextInfo ti : tiArray) {
9999            sbSVG.append(Shape2SVG.Convert(ti, svgStroke,svgFill,svgStrokeWidth,null,null,null));
10000            sbSVG.append("\n");
10001        }
10002
10003        return sbSVG.toString();
10004    }

10006    private static String renderTextElements(ArrayList<TextInfo> tiArray, Color color, Color backgroundColor)
10007    {
10008        String style = null;
10009        String name = RendererSettings.getInstance().getModiferFontProps()[0] + ", sans-serif";//"SansSerif";
10010        String size = RendererSettings.getInstance().getModiferFontProps()[2];
10011        String weight = null;
10012        String anchor = null;//"start";
10013        if(RendererSettings.getInstance().getModiferFont().getTypeface().isBold())
10014            weight = "bold";
10015        StringBuilder sbSVG = new StringBuilder();
10016
10017        String svgStroke = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(RendererUtilities.getIdealOutlineColor(color),false);
10018        if(backgroundColor != null)
10019            svgStroke = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(backgroundColor,false);
10020
10021        String svgFill = RendererUtilities.colorToHexString(color,false);
10022        String svgStrokeWidth = "2";//String.valueOf(RendererSettings.getInstance().getTextOutlineWidth());
10023        sbSVG.append("\n<g");
10024        sbSVG.append(" font-family=\"" + name + '"');
10025        sbSVG.append(" font-size=\"" + size + "px\"");
10026        if(weight != null)
10027            sbSVG.append(" font-weight=\"" + weight + "\"");
10028        sbSVG.append(" alignment-baseline=\"alphabetic\"");//
10029        sbSVG.append(">");
10030
10031        for (TextInfo ti : tiArray) {
10032            sbSVG.append(Shape2SVG.ConvertForGroup(ti, svgStroke,svgFill,svgStrokeWidth,null,null,null));
10033            sbSVG.append("\n");
10034        }
10035        sbSVG.append("</g>\n");
10036
10037        return sbSVG.toString();
10038    }
10039    private static void renderText(Canvas ctx, ArrayList<TextInfo> tiArray, Color color, Color backgroundColor)
10040    {
10041        ModifierRenderer.renderText(ctx, (TextInfo[]) tiArray.toArray(new TextInfo[0]), color, backgroundColor);
10042    }

10044    /**
10045     * 
10046     * @param ctx
10047     * @param tiArray
10048     * @param color
10049     * @param backgroundColor 
10050     */
10051    public static void renderText(Canvas ctx, TextInfo[] tiArray, Color color, Color backgroundColor)
10052    {
10053        /*for (TextInfo textInfo : tiArray) 
10054         {
10055         ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);   
10056         }*/
10057
10058        int size = tiArray.length;
10059
10060        int tbm = RS.getTextBackgroundMethod();
10061        int outlineWidth = RS.getTextOutlineWidth();
10062
10063        if (color == null)
10064        {
10065            color = Color.BLACK;
10066        }
10067
10068        Color outlineColor = null;
10069        
10070        if(backgroundColor != null)
10071            outlineColor = backgroundColor;
10072        else
10073            outlineColor = RendererUtilities.getIdealOutlineColor(color);
10074
10075        if (tbm == RendererSettings.TextBackgroundMethod_OUTLINE_QUICK)
10076        {
10077            synchronized (_ModifierFontMutex) {
10078                //draw text outline
10079                _modifierFont.setStyle(Style.FILL);
10080                _modifierFont.setStrokeWidth(RS.getTextOutlineWidth());
10081                _modifierFont.setColor(outlineColor.toInt());
10082
10083                if (outlineWidth > 2)
10084                    outlineWidth = 2;
10085
10086                if (outlineWidth > 0) {
10087                    for (int i = 0; i < size; i++) {
10088                        TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[i];
10089                        if (outlineWidth > 0) {
10090                            for (int j = 1; j <= outlineWidth; j++) {
10091                                if (j == 1) {
10092                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x - j, textInfo.getLocation().y - j, _modifierFont);
10093                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x + j, textInfo.getLocation().y - j, _modifierFont);
10094                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x - j, textInfo.getLocation().y + j, _modifierFont);
10095                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x + j, textInfo.getLocation().y + j, _modifierFont);
10096
10097                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x - j, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10098                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x + j, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10099
10100                                } else {
10101                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x - j, textInfo.getLocation().y - j, _modifierFont);
10102                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x + j, textInfo.getLocation().y - j, _modifierFont);
10103                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x - j, textInfo.getLocation().y + j, _modifierFont);
10104                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x + j, textInfo.getLocation().y + j, _modifierFont);
10105
10106                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x - j, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10107                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x + j, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10108
10109                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y + j, _modifierFont);
10110                                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y - j, _modifierFont);
10111                                }
10112
10113                            }
10114
10115                        }
10116
10117                    }
10118                }
10119                //draw text
10120                _modifierFont.setColor(color.toInt());
10121
10122                for (int j = 0; j < size; j++) {
10123                    TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[j];
10124                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10125                /*Paint outline = new Paint();
10126                 outline.setStyle(Style.STROKE);
10127                 outline.setColor(Color.red.toInt());
10128                 outline.setAlpha(155);
10129                 outline.setStrokeWidth(1f);
10130                 ctx.drawRect(textInfo.getTextBounds(), outline);
10131                 outline.setColor(Color.blue.toInt());
10132                 ctx.drawRect(textInfo.getTextOutlineBounds(), outline);//*/
10133                }
10134            }
10135        }
10136        else if (tbm == RendererSettings.TextBackgroundMethod_OUTLINE)
10137        {
10138            synchronized (_ModifierFontMutex) {
10139                //draw text outline
10140                //draw text outline
10141                _modifierFont.setStyle(Style.STROKE);
10142                _modifierFont.setStrokeWidth(RS.getTextOutlineWidth());
10143                _modifierFont.setColor(outlineColor.toInt());
10144                if (outlineWidth > 0) {
10145                    for (int i = 0; i < size; i++) {
10146                        TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[i];
10147                        ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10148                    }
10149                }
10150                //draw text
10151                _modifierFont.setColor(color.toInt());
10152                _modifierFont.setStyle(Style.FILL);
10153                for (int j = 0; j < size; j++) {
10154                    TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[j];
10155                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10156                }
10157            }
10158        }
10159        else if (tbm == RendererSettings.TextBackgroundMethod_COLORFILL)
10160        {
10161            synchronized (_ModifierFontMutex) {
10162                Paint rectFill = new Paint();
10163                rectFill.setStyle(Paint.Style.FILL);
10164                rectFill.setColor(outlineColor.toARGB());
10165
10166
10167                //draw rectangle
10168                for (int k = 0; k < size; k++) {
10169                    TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[k];
10170                    ctx.drawRect(textInfo.getTextOutlineBounds(), rectFill);
10171                }
10172                //draw text
10173                _modifierFont.setColor(color.toInt());
10174                _modifierFont.setStyle(Style.FILL);
10175                for (int j = 0; j < size; j++) {
10176                    TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[j];
10177                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10178                }
10179            }
10180        }
10181        else if (tbm == RendererSettings.TextBackgroundMethod_NONE)
10182        {
10183            synchronized (_ModifierFontMutex) {
10184                _modifierFont.setColor(color.toInt());
10185                _modifierFont.setStyle(Style.FILL);
10186                for (int j = 0; j < size; j++) {
10187                    TextInfo textInfo = tiArray[j];
10188                    ctx.drawText(textInfo.getText(), textInfo.getLocation().x, textInfo.getLocation().y, _modifierFont);
10189                }
10190            }
10191        }
10192    }

10194    public static boolean hasDisplayModifiers(String symbolID, Map<String,String> modifiers)
10195    {
10196        boolean hasModifiers = false;
10197        int ss = SymbolID.getSymbolSet(symbolID);
10198        int status = SymbolID.getStatus(symbolID);
10199        int context = SymbolID.getContext(symbolID);
10200
10201        if(ss == SymbolID.SymbolSet_ControlMeasure)//check control measure
10202        {
10203            if (SymbolUtilities.isCBRNEvent(symbolID) == true && modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.Q_DIRECTION_OF_MOVEMENT))
10204            {
10205                hasModifiers = true;
10206            }
10207            else if(SymbolUtilities.hasFDI(symbolID))
10208                hasModifiers = true;
10209        }
10210        else if(ss != SymbolID.SymbolSet_Atmospheric &&
10211                ss != SymbolID.SymbolSet_Oceanographic &&
10212                ss != SymbolID.SymbolSet_MeteorologicalSpace)
10213        {//checking units
10214
10215            if(context > 0) //Exercise or Simulation
10216                hasModifiers = true;
10217
10218            //echelon or mobility,
10219            if (SymbolID.getAmplifierDescriptor(symbolID) > 0 || modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.Q_DIRECTION_OF_MOVEMENT))
10220                hasModifiers = true;
10221
10222            if(modifiers.containsKey(Modifiers.AO_ENGAGEMENT_BAR))
10223                hasModifiers = true;
10224
10225            //HQ/Taskforce
10226            if(SymbolID.getHQTFD(symbolID) > 0)
10227                hasModifiers = true;
10228
10229            if(status > 1)//Fully capable, damaged, destroyed
10230                hasModifiers = true;
10231        }//no display modifiers for single point weather
10232
10233
10234
10235        return hasModifiers;
10236    }
10237
10238    public static boolean hasTextModifiers(String symbolID, Map<String,String> modifiers)
10239    {
10240
10241        int ss = SymbolID.getSymbolSet(symbolID);
10242        int ec = SymbolID.getEntityCode(symbolID);
10243        if(ss == SymbolID.SymbolSet_Atmospheric)
10244        {
10245            switch(ec)
10246            {
10247                case 110102: //tropopause low
10248                case 110202: //tropopause high
10249                case 162200: //tropopause level ?
10250                case 162300: //freezing level ?
10251                    return true;
10252                default:
10253                        return false;
10254            }
10255        }
10256        else if(ss == SymbolID.SymbolSet_Oceanographic || ss == SymbolID.SymbolSet_MeteorologicalSpace)
10257        {
10258            return false;
10259        }
10260        else if (ss == SymbolID.SymbolSet_ControlMeasure)
10261        {
10262            MSInfo msi = MSLookup.getInstance().getMSLInfo(symbolID);
10263
10264            if( msi.getModifiers().size() > 0 && modifiers != null && modifiers.size() > 0)
10265                return true;
10266            else
10267                return false;
10268        }
10269        else
10270        {
10271
10272            if (SymbolUtilities.getStandardIdentityModifier(symbolID) != null)
10273            {
10274                return true;
10275            }
10276
10277            int cc = SymbolID.getCountryCode(symbolID);
10278            if (cc > 0 && GENCLookup.getInstance().get3CharCode(cc) != "")
10279            {
10280                return true;
10281            }//*/
10282
10283            else if (modifiers.size() > 0)
10284            {
10285                return true;
10286            }
10287        }
10288        return false;
10289    }
